Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.99,0:00:03.44,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The season is summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:05.36,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The long-awaited finals are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:08.55,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Every bit of happiness that was inside me is now loitering around Brazil,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:10.36,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and it doesn't look like any of it's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:13.74,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey. Do you know what day it is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:15.44,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:16.37,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.90,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Asahina-san's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:18.94,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.75,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koizumi or Nagato's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.11,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You think I would know their birthdays?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:23.47,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, my birthday is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:24.85,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:29.82,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have no idea how important today is do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:33.13,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All I see is another hot weekday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:36.11,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tell me what day and what month it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.11,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}July 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:42.42,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was hoping for something else, but you're talking about Tanabata, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:45.97,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course I am! It's Tanabata! {TL Note: Asian Valentine's Day.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:49.34,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As a Japanese person, you should never forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.60,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:53.40,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I take festivals like this one very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:57.19,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Starting this year, we're going to have a grand Tanabata with everyone each and every year!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:58.45,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And so it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:07.77,Haruhi Top,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grave: Lead a materialistically simple yet spiritually fulfilling life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:12.80,Title,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(209,48)\fad(760,570)}Bamboo Leaf Rhapsody
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:10.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a law that states that when Haruhi suggests something,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:15.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the rest of us will end up running here, there, front, back and sideways meaninglessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:17.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This law has governed my every day since this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:21.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm starting to hate myself for getting used to this kind of lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.39,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:24.88,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:26.41,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:28.02,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello. How's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:31.73,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've felt like a crazy mess every day since entering high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:33.15,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:35.22,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:36.66,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're most welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.11,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How about a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:40.99,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm getting tired of Othello since we play it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.56,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Unfortunately, I don't know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:44.50,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:47.64,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now's the only time you have to take it easy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.15,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once she comes up with something meaningless again-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:51.96,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yahooooi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:54.30,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}'pologies 'pologies! Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.86,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where did you get that and your greeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:58.20,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The forest behind the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.04,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that private property?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:00.84,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bamboo thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:03.57,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look! I made some paper strips too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.02,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone, write down your wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:06.55,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Paper strips?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:08.26,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see. It's Tanabata today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.90,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, there's a condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.94,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What condition? We haven't even agreed to it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:18.84,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon, do you know who the two responsible for granting the wishes on Tanabata are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:20.65,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aren't they Orihime and Hikoboshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:21.86,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:23.01,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}10 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:26.03,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But do you know which stars Orihime and Hikoboshi are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:26.36,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:27.96,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vega and Altair, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.75,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}85 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:33.12,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Basically, that means your paper strips have to be facing towards those stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.92,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So what happened to the remaining 15 points?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.41,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.55,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}According to the Special Theory of Relativity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.38,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there's no way to go faster than the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:48.05,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, Vega and Altair are 25 and 16 light years away from Earth, respectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.06,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(433,113)\frz20}Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.06,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz10\c&HABB1A0&\pos(591,243)}25 light years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.06,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,43)}Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.06,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,43)}Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.12,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,247)\c&H9AA093&}16 light years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:48.33,Chalk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,247)\c&H9AA093&}{\alpha&HFF&}16 light{\alpha&H00&} years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:49.06,Chalk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,247)\c&H9AA093&}16 light years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:53.59,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz12\fs18\pos(340,31)\c&H949688&}Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:53.59,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz15\pos(465,101)\fs18\c&H7D7C71&}25 light years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:53.59,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(381,201)\c&H808674&}Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:53.59,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\c&H848678&\pos(453,321)}16 light years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:53.59,Chalk,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(599,107)\fs18\c&H605F53&}Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:53.56,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Basically, the time it takes for a message to reach one of those stars is approximately the same amount!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.54,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You looked all that up just for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.75,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that means our wishes won't get granted by those stars until after the time it takes to reach them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.49,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wishes like "I want a boyfriend before Christmas this year" wouldn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:07.38,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:11.30,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}doesn't that mean we're looking at around 50 or 32 years for our wishes to come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:14.54,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They are gods, so they'll do something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.08,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like a 50% off summer bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:17.88,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, what happened to the Theory of Relativity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.60,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take 2 paper strips: one for Altair and one for Vega.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:25.72,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then write down the wishes that you want to come true in 25 and 16 years' time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:30.60,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't even know what I'll be doing in 25 or 16 years' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.94,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell am I supposed to write?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:37.17,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She always comes up with the stupidest things that normal people don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:40.89,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Which universe did her common sense come from anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.83,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't really say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:46.45,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though she acts like that, she knows full well what common sense is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.08,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And how would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.66,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suzumiya-san wishes that the world was considerably different than what it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:56.47,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And she even has the power to rebuild the world from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:04:01.27,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, looking at the world now, I don't think she's lost her sense of reason yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:03.24,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You there! Quit whispering to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.22,Mikuru Sign,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304,244)}I hope I get \nbetter at \ncooking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.22,Mikuru Sign,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(501,297)}I hope I get \nbetter at \nsewing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.76,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think she's misunderstanding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.77,Mikuru Sign,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(325,201)}Harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.77,Mikuru Sign,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(516,149)}Reform
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.89,Mikuru Sign,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(341,149)}Home Safety
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.89,Mikuru Sign,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(492,207)}World Peace
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.89,Mikuru Sign,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,284)}Koizumi Itsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.89,Mikuru Sign,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(489,345)}Koizumi Itsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.06,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mine are just a bit typical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.27,Mikuru Sign,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(533,164)}Give me money
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.27,Mikuru Sign,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(307,340)}Give me a \nbungalow \nthat has \na yard \nwhere I \ncan wash \nmy dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.70,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How plebian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:17.14,Haruhi,Kyou,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.82,Mikuru Sign,Kyou,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(324,227)}Make the world \nrevolve \naround me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.82,Mikuru Sign,Kyou,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(485,312)}I want the \nEarth to \nreverse \nits rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.28,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mine are way better than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.32,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We just have different values.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.95,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone, make sure you remember what you wrote!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.32,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The first checkpoint will be in 16 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:32.11,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a race to see whose wish Hikoboshi grants first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.80,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}16 years, huh... What a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:58.44,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After that, Haruhi seemed to be in abnormally low spirits and had an air of melancholy emanating from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.57,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That sudden quietness of hers was quite disturbing, to say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.22,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's scary to think about her reaction after being so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.49,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Would you like some more tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.90,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, yes please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:19.80,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.21,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.01,Haruhi Top,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Paper strip: After the club's done, please stay in the clubroom - Mikuru
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.22,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your wish is my command!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.22,Haruhi Top,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Book: When You're in Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.27,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.06,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take care of the keys if you're the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.11,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.50,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, you have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.23,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.45,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:55.63,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.38,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm glad we were left alone pretty naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.28,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this something the others shouldn't know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.86,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:09.34,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... there's a place I want to go to with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.34,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right. Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.74,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.93,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.02,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thr-...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.27,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry for saying something weird so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:26.19,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... you don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.35,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you talking about time travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.23,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.78,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have no qualms about going, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.79,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why me? For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:38.49,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, you'll... understand once you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:40.29,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.70,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.88,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't ask any questions and just say okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.76,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or else... I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.60,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.52,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:51.97,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.45,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.43,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:57.83,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.71,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.53,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So damn cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.15,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:10.60,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come to think of it, me believing that she was a time traveler wasn't just based on her word alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.10,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And, speaking of proof, the existence of adult Asahina-san is the only bit of proof I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:19.03,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That would make this quite the perfect chance to see for myself whether she's really from the future or not, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:22.00,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So where's the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.28,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll go from right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:23.67,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.84,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:34.68,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.51,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:46.84,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... if you don't get up soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.40,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my legs are going to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.82,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why was I asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:02.34,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, I can't let you know how to travel through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.75,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.62,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:08.98,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nah, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.18,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it were Haruhi, I'd have punched her already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.40,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But since it's you, Asahina-san, it's all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.61,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.26,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So we're now three years back in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.97,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is July 7th, three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.06,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think it's about 9 o'clock at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.22,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:23.35,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:31.19,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the same park that Nagato called me to last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.35,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this a mecca for weird people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.64,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Asahina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.43,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:50.09,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is she trying to imply something with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.43,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon-kun, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:58.93,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:05.18,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So this is what I looked like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.23,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was her job to guide you to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.54,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}From here on, guiding you will be my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:19.30,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Were you the one who put Asahina-san to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:26.79,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't let her see me since I hadn't seen myself when I was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:32.85,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go down that road and you'll see a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.88,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Help the person who'll be standing in front of the school gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:39.70,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, but please carry my old self over there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:42.20,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This feels like a game event.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.97,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do I get some kind of item as a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.85,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.98,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.61,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't have anything to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:57.79,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you can just steal a kiss from my sleeping self over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.57,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Only when I'm sleeping, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.62,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thats... a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.99,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In terms of my beliefs and the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.62,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}that goes against my values.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.83,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However. Nah. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.29,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's time. I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.53,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And please keep me a secret from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.60,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.34,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pinky promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.16,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pinky promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:24.78,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Goodbye, Kyon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.02,Haruhi,Mikurubig,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:35.36,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder how long it'll be before I meet the adult Asahina-san again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.78,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It feels like she hasn't changed at all since we last met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:42.67,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}More importantly, is this really three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.89,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need to find a way to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.03,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Should I call 117?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.49,School,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(271,147)}East Municipal Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.11,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}East Middle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.45,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.09,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.36,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This really is three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:08.10,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suzumiya Haruhi, at the moment a first year middle school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.91,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I asked you who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:12.27,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A pervert? A kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.44,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:16.27,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't it obvious? I'm illegally trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.94,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't believe you openly declared your criminal intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:23.49,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know who you are, but if you've got time, come and help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.78,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If not, I'll report you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.24,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Haruhi. There's no mistake about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:30.58,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.12,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank goodness it's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.77,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That way she won't be able to get a good look at our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:41.15,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think the Haruhi from three years in the future seemed to have the faintest recollection of us, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.43,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Otherwise, I get the feeling we'd get into trouble if that wasn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:48.24,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hid this stuff after taking it out of storage this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.57,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pretty clever idea, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.88,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll take that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.39,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You grab the line marker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:11:59.82,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So what do you want to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.40,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Draw the lines according to my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:02.82,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.60,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes. You.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.08,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need to be the one directing after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.63,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That line is crooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:11.46,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:15.33,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This girl is calmly ordering around a high school student that she's never even met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:17.76,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just like I thought, that's so Haruhi-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:22.00,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if this was the first time I met this middle school girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I probably would've thought that she's pretty messed in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.72,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, following Haruhi's instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:29.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was running left and right drawing white lines on the sports grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:34.85,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never would've thought that the message Taniguchi was talking about the other day was drawn by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.42,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hm. It's passable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.55,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry it's not perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.90,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you think aliens exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.58,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:47.87,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:49.53,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They do, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:50.95,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about time travelers then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.70,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wouldn't be surprised if they did too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.16,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And espers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.17,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're probably all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:57.33,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People from parallel universes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.46,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I haven't met any yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.19,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's North High's uniform, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:05.21,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.22,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.47,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}John Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:09.68,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.89,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me keep my anonymity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.36,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who were you carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.91,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.33,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She has a sleeping disorder that makes her suddenly fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.52,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She can fall asleep anywhere and anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.00,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I end up carrying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:24.23,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.60,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What exactly is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.08,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:27.70,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.57,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me it's for Orihime and Hikoboshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.08,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.50,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, it's Tanabata.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.06,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You just remind me of someone I know who does this kind of stuff too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.45,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd love to meet that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.26,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there someone like that at North High?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:42.58,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.34,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}North High, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.26,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.77,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've completed what I came to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.27,Haruhi,LoliHaruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:57.77,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not even a word of thanks for all that help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.51,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.44,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-W-W-W-Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.16,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? Why? What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:09.56,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.85,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The TPDD is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:16.54,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.04,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.42,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.27,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's a TPDD?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.59,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's classified so I can't explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.26,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but it's something like a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.89,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How did you lose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.23,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.85,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no way I could've lost it, but I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.68,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there anyone who can come save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.04,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.55,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words, what will happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.47,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll be stuck *hick* here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:50.01,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're stuck on the time plane of three years in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:52.43,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and we can't go back to our own time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.28,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's quite serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.86,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:15:01.12,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But right now, I don't even feel an iota of tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:05.73,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The one who took the TPDD thingy might've been the adult Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.13,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was probably why she came back to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:12.80,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because she herself had already experienced losing the TPDD...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.80,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think we may have a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.03,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this the residence of Nagato Yuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:40.31,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um, I don't really know how to put this myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:46.25,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Would it help if I said that I'm an acquaintance of Suzumiya Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:57.81,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.56,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.23,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's our story, and the reason why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:10.24,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, the you from three years in the future gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:18.58,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:22.80,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This would be the first time you've ever met us, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:23.07,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:27.06,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Requesting access permission for memory of temporal variants in an external time period.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:30.71,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Download of reversible data from linked time planes complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:37.80,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The me from the temporal plane of three years in the future and the present me are now the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.20,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Memory has been shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.22,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.30,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Synchronization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.23,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.18,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you wearing a North High uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.19,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have you enrolled already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:56.47,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No. The me right now is on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.73,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean by standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:00.41,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You mean you will be on standby for three more years?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:00.81,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:03.54,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That a terribly long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:05.17,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:10.71,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is more than one way to move through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:14.75,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The TPDD is just a device for controlling space-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.12,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's unreliable and primitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:18.72,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um, what do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:22.65,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When a TPDD is used to transfer organic matter through time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.43,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there are problems with limited range and noise generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:28.29,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To us that is not perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:31.23,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By "us" you mean the Integrated Data Sentient Entity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:34.61,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nagato-san, you can travel through time with a complete form?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:37.12,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Form is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.32,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All that is required is to be able to transmit the same identity data.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.26,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm taking a wild guess, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.33,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you telling us to sleep here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:56.67,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:58.75,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just Asahina-san and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:17:59.44,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.23,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.38,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Straight to the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:02.85,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.22,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, that's what we were planning to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:11.02,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W- W-Well... it looks like there's no way around this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.15,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.17,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.18,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.22,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that your TPDD?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:53.34,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, this is just a digital watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.14,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank goodness, we're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:19:00.08,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just past 9:30 on the day we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:03.99,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.08,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By freezing a selected set of fluid data in space into stasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:11.49,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then by unfreezing at the corresponding end point in the space-time continuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:13.77,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You mean you stopped time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:14.66,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:18.91,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nagato-san stopped time in this room for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.96,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And today, she unfroze it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:24.42,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:25.32,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.99,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:33.23,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Basically, that means that when I first visited you and heard you talk about aliens and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.96,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Asahina-san and I were sleeping in the next room?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:37.71,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:43.24,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always thought you were hiding your true powers from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.95,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But doesn't this make you invincible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:46.68,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.87,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:49.92,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Emergency mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:52.66,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If there's no need for it, it won't be accessible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:54.63,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:56.15,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.80,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you read what it says?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.35,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.55,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's what's written.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:16.81,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me, but this isn't a real language used by real aliens somewhere is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.69,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nagato didn't answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.28,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forgive me. I... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:29.25,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't really understand myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:31.46,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm an underling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.32,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, a grunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:36.00,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it's because I'm more like a trainee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:38.84,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Despite that, you're close to Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:44.37,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's only because no one thought that I would be the one Suzumiya-san would catch and pull into her club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:53.03,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My superiors, or maybe even the higher-ups as well, just give me orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:56.15,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and I move according to those orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:21:01.81,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I don't even know the meaning behind some of the things I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.90,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The superior is the adult Asahina-san, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:12.30,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That adult version of Asahina-san probably knows what's going to happen to us already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:16.31,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it doesn't look like she told this Asahina-san anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.77,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:21.43,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People from the future also have their own rules and laws I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:25.27,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone will tell me everything someday, once everything has settled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:28.91,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:30.77,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words, the 8th of July.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:33.39,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In my head, it's just the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:37.06,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But to my body, it feels like three years have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.92,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong? Did you eat something poisonous or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.02,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:47.15,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just melancholy from reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:50.41,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've got some memories of Tanabata from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.41,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:58.89,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Nagato, Asahina-san actually is from the future, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:21:59.16,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:00.99,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:04.76,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I get the feeling that there's a lack of consistency regarding the ability to travel through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:06.47,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:11.24,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Asahina-san once told me that there was no continuity between the past and the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:16.02,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I went back three years and granted Haruhi some of my wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:22.50,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and it seems like there's a distinct possibility that those ideas brought her to North High to look for people who...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:24.69,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}aren't "just humans".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:29.62,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This means that there's continuity between the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.95,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that contrary to what Asahina-san said?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:37.46,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A standard axiomatic theory cannot be used to prove the existence of a paradox within a given incident itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.96,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That might've been an explanation by your standards, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:43.84,Haruhi,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll understand eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:50.80,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:55.40,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right now, my king is being checked by your rook.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:58.92,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is troublesome. Where should I run to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:05.72,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, now where's the paradox in me doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:11.07,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Besides, a king doesn't really mean much to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:14.08,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The queen is the most important up until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:15.77,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:18.34,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've got no idea what's going to happen next,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:21.72,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I just want something that won't give me a headache to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:24.12,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think peace and quiet is best,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:26.59,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but would you prefer something to happen instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:31.03,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You troublemaker.
